@palpatim notes:

FWIW, we also notify on "connecting" and "disconnected" states. "Connecting" isn't terribly meaningful, and "disconnected" degrades to a completion on the subscription data publisher, so that may not be necessary in Android

Not sure if we need to do this today -- or can defer.

